<br>
Soloing to gain levels, which usually compromises of staying in one or two select areas, usually killing the same (or similar) mobs over and over and over and over and over, has to be the most boring thing ever.<br>
<br>
Ala fungus grove, soloing velks ent, seb, places you're used to doing it, where its fast xp, usually easy and not too dangerous.<br>
<br>
Soloing one of the wings in HS: possible to do, but hard, risky, very dangerous. but a TON of fun. Trying to break Freeti room solo, fun. farming skyfire or fungus grove for some xp day after day, grouping little or none of the time, please whack me over the head with a sledgehammer, heh. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=14427">Lauralan of the Nexus</a>, 60th Warlock<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=21609">Tyros Darkheart</a>, 60th Warlord<br>Lorean Korath, 53rd Vicar.<br><Mortalis> Antonius Bayle</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uelessarelfstone.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elessar Elfstone</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/20/02 9:17:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22859.topic&index=72>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.cogeco.ca/~dominance/elessars/bender2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Umm yes</span><hr size=1> Fair enough<br>
